How to Become a Member?

American Educational Institute is selling Memberships for their Students,Professors,Admins and Staff. Memberships are classified as "Student Membership" and "Professional Membership". AIE allows you to donate Funds to "Askland Memorial Scholarship" and " Save the Whales"(Donation Levels are derived based on the Type of Fund/Donation Program)

To Become a Member:

  1. A User must be Authenticated to purchase a Membership.
  2. A User must fill the Membership Application Form and make sure that the required fields are completely filled
  3. Membership Type is Derived based on the Role Specified on the Membership Application.

(If the Role is Student then the User will be able to purchase a Student Membership and If the Role is Admin/Professor/Staff,

then the User will be able to purchase a Professional Membership).

4.User can donate if you wish to make a donation.



About American Educational Institute

American Educational Institute (AEI), established in 1969, is the premier provider of self-study programs in insurance claims law. Courses are practical, flexible, and interactive. Programs in: Legal Principles, Liability, Property, Workers' Compensation, Fraud Investigation and Defense, and Automobile lead to industry-recognized designations including AEI's highest, the Senior Claim Law Associate (SCLA). Courses are approved for continuing education credit toward adjuster license renewal in many states and college credit by the National College Credit Recommendation Service.
You must be logged in to become a member. Create an Account here if you do not have an Account with AIE.

Company Membership


The Company Membership is the perfect membership option for organizations such as nonprofits, government agencies, and start-ups that operate in the edtech marketplace. Our Company Members seek to build relationships with education leaders and want to share their expertise. Company Membership opens the door to communication and collaboration within the vibrant ISTE community.


Are you an individual in the field seeking to connect? We also offer Professional and Individual Memberships.


Please note that you must create an account and be logged in to purchase a membership.

We're Here to Help.

Your patients count on you to give them the best care, now count on the International Association give you the tools and resources to focus your time where it matters most. When you join the International Association , you gain a network that’s committed to:

  • Advancing the specialty of family medicine
  • Strengthening members’ collective voice
  • Providing solutions to enhance patient care

What Is Your Membership Worth?

As a member, you will receive a variety of exclusive products, programs, services, and discounts totaling nearly $3,000 in member savings.


Learn More About Member Value

The International Association represents 131,400 physicians and medical students nationwide, as the only medical society devoted solely to primary care. Family physicians conduct approximately one in five office visits -- that’s 192 million visits annually or 48 percent more than the next most visited medical specialty.

As a member, not only will you help advance this important specialty, but you’ll also have exclusive access to our CME reporting service, discounts on hundreds of courses and products, and leading-edge career and practice support.
